OL,3,CMP who 'did GCSE revision in B&B'
OL,4,Cbacks homeless pledge
OL,6,FA formerly homeless MP has welcomed
OL,7,Fthe Government's pledge to halve the
OL,8,Fnumber of long-term rough sleepers.
OL,10,FLee Pitcher, the Labour MP for
OL,11,FDoncaster, told the Commons he had
OL,12,Fspent time revising for his GCSEs on
OL,13,Fthe floor of a bed and breakfast (B&B)
OL,14,Fhe was staying in temporarily.
