OL,3,CMP who 'did GCSE revision in B&B'
OL,4,Cbacks homeless pledge
OL,6,FSpeaking after the government
OL,7,Fannounced a pledge to end the illegal
OL,8,Fuse of B&Bs for families, he said:
OL,9,F"This is deeply, deeply personal to
OL,10,Fme, because I was one of those
OL,11,Fchildren 34 years ago sat on a double
OL,12,Fmattress, in a room, doing my GCSE
OL,13,Frevision, my coursework, and then
OL,14,Fhaving to sleep next to my mum and
OL,15,Fsister in a room while all that was
OL,16,Fgoing on.
OL,26,@qD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
