OL,3,CMP who 'did GCSE revision in B&B'
OL,4,Cbacks homeless pledge
OL,6,F"That's why today is so remarkably
OL,7,Fimportant and I'm so proud to stand
OL,8,Fhere and be able to hear that we are
OL,9,Fgoing to do something about this,
OL,10,Fbecause I can tell this House when
OL,11,Fthat happens to you, you feel alone,
OL,12,Fyou feel isolated, you feel no-one
OL,13,Fcares, and your dignity and your self-
OL,14,Frespect sits in somebody else's hands."
OL,16,FMost recent figures show there were
OL,17,F2,070 households in England with
OL,18,Fchildren at the end of June in
OL,19,Ftemporary B&B accommodation for longer
OL,20,Fthan the statutory limit of six weeks.
