OL,3,CMP who 'did GCSE revision in B&B'
OL,4,Cbacks homeless pledge
OL,6,FCommunities minister Alison McGovern
OL,7,Fappeared emotional as she described
OL,8,Fthe MP for Doncaster East and the Isle
OL,9,Fof Axholme as a "champion" for
OL,10,Fchildren living in temporary
OL,11,Faccommodation.
OL,13,FShe added: "This has been a matter of
OL,14,Flife and death ` 1,142 people died
OL,15,Fwhilst homeless last year.
OL,17,F"Everyone deserves a roof over their
OL,18,Fhead, and children, in the worst
OL,19,Fhousing our country can offer, deserve
OL,20,Fthe attention of this House."
