OL,3,CMP who 'did GCSE revision in B&B'
OL,4,Cbacks homeless pledge
OL,6,FAfter being pressed on the
OL,7,Fgovernment's timeline, Ms McGovern
OL,8,Fsaid: "We will end the use of B&B
OL,9,Faccommodation by the end of the
OL,10,Fparliament, in all but the most
OL,11,Fextreme cases, an absolute emergency.
OL,13,F"But, you know, it's already the law
OL,14,Fthat children are not supposed to be
OL,15,Fin B&Bs for more than six weeks. It's
OL,16,Fbeen the law for 20 years. So, what on
OL,17,Fearth is going on in this country when
OL,18,Fthere are 2,000 children in such a
OL,19,Fsituation?"
OL,26,@pD@GOUuD@AOU
