OL,4,Cbacks homeless pledge
OL,6,FThe government said results could be
OL,7,Fexpected by the end of the current
OL,8,Fparliament.
OL,10,FLabour MP Danny Beales, who represents
OL,11,FUxbridge and South Ruislip, who spent
OL,12,Ftime as a teenager without a home,
OL,13,Fthanked the government adding the move
OL,14,Fwas "long overdue".
OL,16,FMs McGovern replied: "This House is so
OL,17,Fmuch the better for having people in
OL,18,Fit that actually know what we're
OL,19,Ftalking about today."
